  People love to try and take the moral high ground.By declaring that, "their beliefs are facts". Whileeveryone else's are uncertain ideas, with no foundation in reality.   Belief is all we got Jon. Scientist regularly use the word in their writings. Science even admits, scientific FACTS aren't like, every day facts. They aren't absolutely certain.   So it is after all. Your belief verses someone else's. 